{"service_name": "Information Security, Risk Management and Information Assurance", "service_id": "7459342601139827", "company_name": "Empiric Solutions Limited", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Empiric Solutions Limited\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Information Security, Risk Management and Information Assurance\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    We provide Information Security recruitment services providing candidates specilaisning in the following specialisms of Information Security;\r\n\r\nInformation Security Management\r\nInformation Assurance and Governance\r\nRisk Management\r\nRegularity Compliance\r\nSecurity Audit\r\nBusiness Continuity and Disaster Recovery\r\nData Loss Prevention (DLP)\r\nIdentity and Access Management (IAM / IdM)\r\nSecurity Training and Awareness\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Highly skill Information Security Consultants\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Network security vulnerability scanning and firewall configuration\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Consultants focusing on auditing of secure systems\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Identity and access mangemnt and access control\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Data loss prevention principles and techniques\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Skilled penetration testers and vulnerability scanning specilaists\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Business continuity and disaster recovery planning\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Information security governance, risk and compliance management\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Information security training and awareness and security policy\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Third party risk assurance and assessment of third party usage\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Ensure networks are safe secure by way technical security testing\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Ensure information security risks are understood and mitigated\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Ensure staff awareness of security risks through training and awareness\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Cost saving of security budgets by providing expert gap analysis\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Ensure data protention through data loss prevention startergy\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Ensuring compliance to all relevant security standards\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Management of information projects and programmes\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Implementation of disaster recovering planning methodologies\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Management and auditing of existing security functions\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3450 to \u00a31500 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/584997/7459342601139827-pricing-document-2015-10-06-1333.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/584997/7459342601139